<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>TP N°4 · Funciones</title>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#0a1628;
  --hero1:#0d2137; --hero2:#1a3a5c;
  --card-bg:#0d2137; --card-border:#1e3a55;
  --opt-bg:#0a1f35; --opt-hover:#0d2a45;
  --correct-bg:#0a2e1a; --correct-input:#0d2e17; --correct-border:#4ade80;
  --incorrect-bg:#2e0a0a; --incorrect-input:#2e1515; --incorrect-border:#f87171;
  --plane-bg:#f8f9ff; --grid:#dde3f0;
  --text:#e7edf5; --text-dim:#8fa3bf;
  --radius:14px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Segoe UI',system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.55;}
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d2137,#1a3a5c,#0d2137);padding:44px 20px 30px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--card-border);}
.hero .eyebrow{color:#7dd3fc;font-size:12.5px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px;}
.hero h1{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:clamp(22px,4.5vw,34px);background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00d4aa,#3b82f6);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;font-weight:800;}
.hero p{margin:4px 0;color:var(--text-dim);font-size:14.5px;max-width:560px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;}
.hero .badge{display:inline-block;margin-top:14px;padding:6px 14px;background:#0a1f35;border:1px solid var(--card-border);border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;color:#00d4aa;letter-spacing:.5px;}

.progress-wrap{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;background:#0d2137;padding:10px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--card-border);}
.progress-track{flex:1;height:10px;background:#1e3a55;border-radius:999px;overflow:hidden;}
.progress-fill{height:100%;width:0%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00d4aa,#3b82f6);transition:width .4s ease;border-radius:999px;}
.progress-label{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-dim);min-width:70px;text-align:right;}

.toc{position:sticky;top:46px;z-index:40;background:#0a1628;padding:9px 16px;display:flex;gap:7px;overflow-x:auto;border-bottom:1px solid var(--card-border);}
.toc a{flex:0 0 auto;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:#0d2137;border:1px solid var(--card-border);color:var(--text-dim);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:11.5px;text-decoration:none;transition:.2s;}
.toc a:hover{background:#0d2a45;color:#00d4aa;border-color:#00d4aa;}
.toc a.done{background:#0a2e1a;border-color:#4ade80;color:#4ade80;}

main{max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:22px 14px 60px;}
.card{background:#0d2137;border:1px solid #1e3a55;border-radius:var(--radius);padding:20px 20px 22px;margin-bottom:20px;}
.card:not(.final-card){content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:1px 640px;}
.card-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:4px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.card-num{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00d4aa,#3b82f6);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-weight:800;color:#06141f;font-size:14px;flex:0 0 auto;}
.card-title{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin:0;}
.dyn-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;color:#00d4aa;background:#0a2e2a;border:1px solid #14513f;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;}
.statement{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 14px;padding:11px 13px;background:#0a1f35;border-left:3px solid #3b82f6;border-radius:8px;}
.statement b{color:#cfe0f5;}
.sub{margin:16px 0 6px;font-weight:600;color:#cfe0f5;font-size:14px;}

.field-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;margin:7px 0;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.field-row label{font-size:13.5px;color:var(--text-dim);min-width:170px;}
.ans-input{background:#0d2137;border:1px solid #2b4863;color:var(--text);padding:7px 9px;border-radius:8px;font-size:13.5px;width:100px;}
.ans-input:focus{outline:none;border-color:#3b82f6;}
.ans-input.correct{background:var(--correct-input);border-color:var(--correct-border);color:#bbf7d0;}
.ans-input.incorrect{background:var(--incorrect-input);border-color:var(--incorrect-border);color:#fecaca;}

.choice-group{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:7px 0;}
.choice-btn,.match-btn{background:var(--opt-bg);border:1px solid #1e3a55;color:var(--text);padding:8px 13px;border-radius:9px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;transition:.15s;}
.choice-btn:hover,.match-btn:hover{background:var(--opt-hover);}
.choice-btn.selected,.match-btn.selected{border-color:#3b82f6;background:#0d2a45;}
.choice-btn.correct,.match-btn.correct{background:var(--correct-bg);border-color:var(--correct-border);color:#bbf7d0;}
.choice-btn.incorrect,.match-btn.incorrect{background:var(--incorrect-bg);border-color:var(--incorrect-border);color:#fecaca;}
.match-btn.locked{opacity:.55;cursor:default;}

.verify-btn{margin-top:12px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00d4aa,#3b82f6);color:#06141f;border:none;padding:10px 18px;border-radius:9px;font-weight:700;font-size:13.5px;cursor:pointer;}
.verify-btn:hover{filter:brightness(1.08);}

.feedback-msg{display:none;margin-top:12px;padding:10px 13px;border-radius:9px;font-size:13.5px;border:1px solid;}
.feedback-msg.success{background:var(--correct-bg);border-color:#4ade8055;color:#bbf7d0;}
.feedback-msg.error{background:var(--incorrect-bg);border-color:#f8717155;color:#fecaca;}

table.fill-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:10px 0;}
table.fill-table th, table.fill-table td{border:1px solid #1e3a55;padding:7px 9px;text-align:center;font-size:13px;}
table.fill-table th{background:#0a1f35;color:#9fc1e0;}

.mini-plane{width:100%;max-width:300px;display:block;margin:10px auto;border-radius:8px;}
.graph-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:12px;margin:12px 0;}
.graph-card{background:#0a1f35;border:1px solid #1e3a55;border-radius:10px;padding:10px;text-align:center;}
.graph-card .choice-group{justify-content:center;}
.graph-card p{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);margin:4px 0 6px;}

.drop-zones{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-top:12px;}
.drop-zone{min-height:130px;background:#0a1f35;border:2px dashed #2b4863;border-radius:12px;padding:10px;}
.drop-zone h4{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text-dim);text-align:center;}
.drag-card{background:#0d2137;border:1px solid #2b4863;padding:9px 11px;border-radius:9px;margin-bottom:7px;cursor:pointer;font-size:12.5px;transition:.15s;}
.drag-card:hover{border-color:#3b82f6;}
.drag-card.selected{border-color:#00d4aa;background:#0d2a3f;}
.drag-card.placed-correct{background:var(--correct-bg);border-color:var(--correct-border);cursor:default;}
.drag-card.placed-wrong{background:var(--incorrect-bg);border-color:var(--incorrect-border);}
.hint-text{font-size:12px;color:#7dd3fc;margin-top:8px;}

.match-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-top:12px;}
.match-col .match-btn{display:block;width:100%;text-align:left;margin-bottom:7px;font-family:Consolas,monospace;font-size:12.5px;}
.match-col h5{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-dim);margin:0 0 8px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;}

.item-block{border-top:1px dashed #1e3a55;padding-top:14px;margin-top:14px;}
.item-block:first-child{border-top:none;margin-top:0;padding-top:0;}
.func-label{font-family:Consolas,monospace;color:#7dd3fc;font-size:13.5px;background:#0a1f35;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:6px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:10px;}

.final-card{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a2e2a,#0a1f35);text-align:center;border:1px solid #14513f;}
.final-card h2{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:4px;}
.final-stat{font-size:42px;font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#00d4aa,#3b82f6);-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;}
.final-card p{color:var(--text-dim);font-size:13.5px;}

footer{text-align:center;color:#4b6178;font-size:11.5px;padding:20px;}

@media(max-width:560px){
  .field-row label{min-width:100%;}
  .match-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .drop-zones{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="eyebrow">Seminario Nivelatorio de Matemática · INSPT‑UTN</div>
  <h1>Trabajo Práctico N°4: Funciones</h1>
  <p>Unidad 4 — Variables, dominio, funciones lineales, cuadráticas y polinómicas de grado 3. </p> <p>Resolvé cada ejercicio y recibí retroalimentación inmediata.</p>
  <span class="badge">17 ejercicios · feedback al instante</span>
</header>

<div class="progress-wrap">
  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div></div>
  <span class="progress-label" id="progressLabel">0 / 17</span>
</div>
<nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>

<main id="mainEl">

<!-- EJERCICIO 1 -->
<section class="card" id="ej1" data-idx="1">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">1</div><h3 class="card-title">¿Es función?</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Arrastrar y clasificar</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Dadas las siguientes relaciones, indicá cuáles corresponden a <b>funciones</b>. Hacé clic en cada tarjeta y luego en la caja correcta.</div>
  <div id="ej1-cards"></div>
  <div class="drop-zones">
    <div class="drop-zone" id="zone-fn" data-zone="fn"><h4>✅ Es función</h4></div>
    <div class="drop-zone" id="zone-nofn" data-zone="nofn"><h4>❌ No es función</h4></div>
  </div>
  <p class="hint-text" id="ej1-hint"></p>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 2 -->
<section class="card" id="ej2" data-idx="2">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">2</div><h3 class="card-title">Funciones a partir de gráficas</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Opción múltiple</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Dadas las siguientes gráficas, indicá cuáles corresponden a funciones <b>f : ℝ → ℝ</b>. Recordá el criterio de la recta vertical: si una recta vertical corta a la curva en más de un punto, no es función.</div>
  <div class="graph-grid">
    <div class="graph-card">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 150 150" class="mini-plane"><rect width="150" height="150" fill="#f8f9ff"/><line x1="0" y1="75" x2="150" y2="75" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="75" y1="0" x2="75" y2="150" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><circle cx="75" cy="75" r="40" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
      <p>Gráfica a)</p>
      <div class="choice-group" id="g2a"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="graph-card">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 150 150" class="mini-plane"><rect width="150" height="150" fill="#f8f9ff"/><line x1="0" y1="75" x2="150" y2="75" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="75" y1="0" x2="75" y2="150" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="10" y1="140" x2="140" y2="10" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
      <p>Gráfica b)</p>
      <div class="choice-group" id="g2b"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="graph-card">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 150 150" class="mini-plane"><rect width="150" height="150" fill="#f8f9ff"/><line x1="0" y1="75" x2="150" y2="75" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="75" y1="0" x2="75" y2="150" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M130,10 Q90,20 30,75 Q90,130 130,140" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
      <p>Gráfica c)</p>
      <div class="choice-group" id="g2c"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="graph-card">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 150 150" class="mini-plane"><rect width="150" height="150" fill="#f8f9ff"/><line x1="0" y1="75" x2="150" y2="75" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><line x1="75" y1="0" x2="75" y2="150" stroke="#dde3f0" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M15,130 C45,30 65,30 75,75 C85,120 105,120 135,20" fill="none" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="3"/></svg>
      <p>Gráfica d)</p>
      <div class="choice-group" id="g2d"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 3 -->
<section class="card" id="ej3" data-idx="3">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">3</div><h3 class="card-title">Expresar y tabular funciones</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Completar</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Escribí una expresión que represente cada función (aclarando el dominio). Luego completá la tabla de valores.</div>

  <div class="item-block">
    <p class="sub">a) y es el cubo de un número real x.</p>
    <div class="field-row"><label>Expresión:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e3a-expr"></div></div>
    <div class="field-row"><label>Dominio:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e3a-dom"></div></div>
    <table class="fill-table"><tr><th>x</th><th>-1/2</th><th>0</th><th>1</th></tr>
      <tr><td>y</td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e3a-y1" style="width:70px"></td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e3a-y2" style="width:70px"></td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e3a-y3" style="width:70px"></td></tr>
    </table>
  </div>

  <div class="item-block">
    <p class="sub">b) y es el consecutivo del doble de un número entero x.</p>
    <div class="field-row"><label>Expresión:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e3b-expr"></div></div>
    <div class="field-row"><label>Dominio:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e3b-dom"></div></div>
    <table class="fill-table"><tr><th>x</th><th>-1/2</th><th>0</th><th>1</th></tr>
      <tr><td>y</td>
        <td><div class="choice-group" id="e3b-y1" style="justify-content:center"></div></td>
        <td><input class="ans-input" id="e3b-y2" style="width:70px"></td>
        <td><input class="ans-input" id="e3b-y3" style="width:70px"></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="3">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e3-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 4 -->
<section class="card" id="ej4" data-idx="4">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">4</div><h3 class="card-title">f(x) = 2x² − x + 1</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Completar</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Sea f : ℝ → ℝ / f(x) = 2x² − x + 1.</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Calculá f(2):</label><input class="ans-input" id="e4a"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) Valores de x cuya imagen es 1:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e4b-x1" placeholder="x₁"><input class="ans-input" id="e4b-x2" placeholder="x₂"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>c) Imagen del opuesto de 1 — f(−1):</label><input class="ans-input" id="e4c"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>d) ¿Existe x tal que f(x) = −1?</label><div class="choice-group" id="e4d"></div></div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="4">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e4-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 5 -->
<section class="card" id="ej5" data-idx="5">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">5</div><h3 class="card-title">Lectura de un gráfico</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Mixta</span></div>
  <div class="statement">A continuación se presenta la gráfica de una función f : Df → ℝ. Observala con atención y respondé.</div>
  <div id="e5-graph"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Dominio de la función:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e5a"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) Raíces de f:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e5b-x1" placeholder="x₁"><input class="ans-input" id="e5b-x2" placeholder="x₂"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>c) Imagen de −2 — f(−2):</label><input class="ans-input" id="e5c"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>d) ¿Existe x tal que f(x) = −3?</label><div class="choice-group" id="e5d"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>&nbsp;&nbsp;Si es sí, indicá los valores:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e5d-x1" placeholder="x₁"><input class="ans-input" id="e5d-x2" placeholder="x₂"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>e) Ordenada al origen:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e5e"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>f) Conjunto imagen de f:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e5f"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>g) Valor de f(−1/2):</label><input class="ans-input" id="e5g"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>h) ¿Pasa por el punto (1; −4)?</label><div class="choice-group" id="e5h"></div></div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="5">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e5-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 6 -->
<section class="card" id="ej6" data-idx="6">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">6</div><h3 class="card-title">f(x) = 1/x</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Completar</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Sea f : Df → ℝ / f(x) = 1/x.</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Dominio más amplio posible:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e6a"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) Preimagen de 3:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e6b"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>c) ¿Tiene raíces la función?</label><div class="choice-group" id="e6c"></div></div>
  <table class="fill-table"><tr><th>x</th><th>-3/4</th><th>-1</th><th>2</th></tr>
    <tr><td>y</td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e6d-y1" style="width:70px"></td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e6d-y2" style="width:70px"></td><td><input class="ans-input" id="e6d-y3" style="width:70px"></td></tr>
  </table>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="6">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e6-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 7 -->
<section class="card" id="ej7" data-idx="7">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">7</div><h3 class="card-title">Uvas a $4500 el kilo</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Completar</span></div>
  <div class="statement">En una verdulería, el kilo de uvas se vende a $4500.</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Expresión de p en función de c:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e7a"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) ¿La relación entre c y p es función?</label><div class="choice-group" id="e7b-fn"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>&nbsp;&nbsp;Dominio:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e7b-dom"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>c) Kilos comprados si pagó $7425:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e7c"> kg</div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="7">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e7-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 8 -->
<section class="card" id="ej8" data-idx="8">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">8</div><h3 class="card-title">Trote a velocidad constante</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Completar + gráfico</span></div>
  <div class="statement">Una persona trota a velocidad constante de 8,2 km/h. t = tiempo (horas), d = distancia recorrida (km).</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Expresión de d en función de t:</label><div class="choice-group" id="e8a"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) Distancia recorrida en 20 min (1/3 h):</label><input class="ans-input" id="e8b"> km</div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="8">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e8-msg"></div>
  <p class="sub">c) Gráfico de la función:</p>
  <div id="e8-graph"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 9 -->
<section class="card" id="ej9" data-idx="9">
  <div class="card-head"><div class="card-num">9</div><h3 class="card-title">Movimiento de una partícula</h3><span class="dyn-tag">Lectura de gráfico</span></div>
  <div class="statement">t = tiempo (segundos), d = distancia recorrida (metros). Observá el gráfico d(t):</div>
  <div id="e9-graph"></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>a) Dominio de d(t):</label><div class="choice-group" id="e9a"></div></div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>b) Distancia luego de 2 s:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e9b"> m</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>c) ¿Cuánto tardó en recorrer 12 m?</label><input class="ans-input" id="e9c"> s</div>
  <div class="field-row"><label>d) Distancia total recorrida:</label><input class="ans-input" id="e9d"> m</div>
  <button class="verify-btn" data-check="9">Verificar respuestas</button>
  <div class="feedback-msg" id="e9-msg"></div>
</section>

<!-- EJERCICIO 10 -->
<section class="card" id="ej10" data-idx="10">
